$interpreted: Skinny Hunter: We caught so many in just the first day. This is awesome!
Poor Hunter: According to Boss Simon, both frogodile skins and Platypus meats can be sold at great prices!
Skinny Hunter: Haha, looks like we can retire and live a good life once we get this deal done!
Hestia: According to that Platypus, the humans have taken all the animals they captured and locked them here.
Karnulla: Those damn humans...how dare they make my home their base? I will make them pay for this travesty!
Hestia: From the looks of it, there really are quite a few of them. So, what is the plan now?
Karnulla: Their boss is some guy by the name of Simon.
Karnulla: He should be hiding inside at the deepest part. As long as we deal with him, this group of humans will panic and run away instantly.
Hestia: Very well. Then we will lure the people outside away. Once we've dealt with them, we'll charge inside and kick Simon's sorry rump!
Karnulla: Sounds pretty good. How are we going to lure the people outside away though?
Karnulla: Hey, you're not serious about...
Karnulla: You stinkin mermaid~~~! I will get you back for this!
Skinny Hunter: It's the big frogodile that escaped!
Poor Hunter: You're not getting away this time!
Karnulla: Hmph, alright then.
Karnulla: Hey, you want to capture me, don't you? Then you better come after me!
Karnulla: This place should be far enough away, right?
Karnulla: Okay, time for you puny humans to see what I am truly capable of!
Skinny Hunter: D-Didn't think it would be this powerful. What we do now?
Poor Hunter: Most important thing is to stay alive. You die, you lose everything, so RUN!
Karnulla: Hmph, worthless trash!
Karnulla: All done here. I wonder how things are going for that stinkin mermaid? Better go back and take a look.
